        "id": "cadence_interpretation",
        "type": "markdown",
        "layout": "full",
        "sourceId": "runtime_journal",
        "body": "轮询从约 62 秒缩短到约 5 秒是实质改善，但新 cadence 尚无 trade-ready 样本可验证端到端延迟，5 秒 scheduler cadence 也不等于实时交易。当前热路径仍会在持久化 virtual action 前执行同步推理/通知，并与慢任务共享 worker；action 还可能复用服务开头捕获的旧时间，形成 TOCTOU 风险。"
      },
      {
        "id": "gth_diagnosis",
        "type": "markdown",
        "layout": "full",
        "sourceId": "strict_backtest",
        "body": "## GTH 不是靠放宽 stale quote 修复\n\nGTH dip/reclaim 已有 6 个 legacy 信号，但 forward-v3 exact two-leg entry 为 0。旧 virtual open 缺 provider、source timestamp、bid/ask 和 exact spread legs，不能证明真实成交。5 秒 freshness 应继续 hard；在 pending 阶段预订阅目标 long/short 两腿并保持 hot lane，同时 shadow 记录 5/10/15 秒覆盖率。"
      },
      {
        "id": "gate_disposition_block",
        "type": "table",
        "layout": "full",
        "tableId": "gate_disposition_table"
      },
      {
        "id": "gate_interpretation",
        "type": "markdown",
        "layout": "full",
        "sourceId": "runtime_code",
        "body": "把 option structure、候选或行情暂缺改为 pending_data 并在 TTL 内重试；把方向/regime 归入 rejected_strategy；schema、TTL、coordinate、expiry、exact NBBO、freshness 和 max loss 继续 blocked_safety。只有软策略门进入 shadow counterfactual，不能用缺数据来证明策略太严。"
      },
      {
        "id": "execution_slo_block",
